<A>__{from out of the bamboo grove comes ashema, her hands in front of her and her head down. she is not sure drew wants to see her. drew looks at her, then back to san de, but he is already gone. they are alone. drew walks to her, takes her chin in his hand and tilts it up to look at her face. her eyes are full of love and tenderness, and a little fear. drew kisses that fear away.}
